           SHORT="frontend for xine-lib"

cat << EOF
gxine is a frontend for xine which is a free video player. It plays mpeg-2
and mpeg-1 video, DVDs (unlocked/unencrypted only), video CDs, SVCDs,
and AVI files (using Win32 codecs) with synchronized audio and video,
and optionally fullscreen using the Xv extensions in X.
EOF
